OL,3,CScotland's block grant falls to lowest
OL,4,Cshare of UK spending in a decade `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FScotland's block grant has fallen to
OL,8,Fits lowest share of UK Government
OL,9,Fspending in nearly a decade, a report
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FAnalysis by the House of Commons
OL,13,FLibrary, commissioned by the SNP,
OL,14,Fshowed that the proportion of
OL,15,FWestminster spending on Holyrood has
OL,16,Fdecreased from 8.2% in 2015/16 to 7.6%
OL,17,Fas of July this year.
