OL,3,CScotland's block grant falls to lowest
OL,4,Cshare of UK spending in a decade `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe SNP said this meant Scotland's
OL,8,Fblock grant was worth #6.4 billion
OL,9,Fless than it was in 2020/21 ` a drop
OL,10,Fof 12.7%.
OL,12,FThe figures were calculated before any
OL,13,Fadjustments were made to reflect the
OL,14,Fdevolution of tax and welfare powers
OL,15,Fto the Scottish Parliament.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Government has said its
OL,18,Fcapital budget has already been cut by
OL,19,F9.6% ` about #600 million after being
OL,20,Fadjusted for inflation ` while another
OL,21,F3% cut is on its way this year.
