OL,7,FThe capital budget is set aside for
OL,8,Fspending on longer-term projects such
OL,9,Fas buildings and infrastructure like
OL,10,Froads.
OL,12,FThe SNP said that came at the same as
OL,13,FHolyrood's resource budget, which pays
OL,14,Ffor day-to-day spending on things such
OL,15,Fas the NHS, has been cut by nearly 15%
OL,16,Fin real terms since 2020.
OL,18,FThe party urged the Chancellor, who
OL,19,Fwill soon deliver her first Budget
OL,20,Fsince Labour won the election in July,
OL,21,Fto reverse the cuts.
